          "682: Shrubland / Arbustes",
          "#cd9f72",
          "685: Wetland Treed / Zone humide boisée",
          "#adffce",
          "687: Coniferous Forest / Forêt de conifères",
          "#34ebb4",
          "691: Deciduous Forest / Forêt de feuillus",
